evo-to-wc
Converts evolution content to web component equivalents

Properties:

  * `courseicons` {`{ assessment: string; brainstorm: string; casestudy: string; discussion: string; email: string; game: string; group: string; handson: string; image: string; mobile: string; presentation: string; reading: string; ... 8 more ...; yammer: string; }`} - icon conversions

  * `headings` {`string[]`} - list of headings to simplify selectors
